venue.name: Jennifer's House

item.description:
Hi All,

 

Thought it maybe a good idea to get a potluck for the Fall season to enjoy some good home cooked food. I can make the main dish if others want to bring things. My place isn't huge, but I can hold a decent amount. If there's interest feel free to post. I'm putting a 20 rsvp limit on it due to space.

 

Please post what you're bringing of if you need me to have any dishes or plates available. I'll send out my address and phone number to the RSVPs. If you have any questions please let me know.

 

Jennifer
item.name: Potluck!
